    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港融资成本飙升 人民币做空者受压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/offshore-yuan-borrowing-costs-surge-as-currency-support-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港人民币融资成本飙升至多年未见的水平，表明人们担心北京方面稳定人民币的努力可能会导致离岸市场流动性收紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/offshore-yuan-borrowing-costs-surge-as-currency-support-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:49:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球最大微电网公司计划募资 4 亿美元并进行 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/world-s-biggest-mini-grid-firm-aims-to-raise-400-million-plans-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的太阳能微电网运营商 Husk Power Systems 今年计划通过债务和股权融资方式筹集高达 4 亿美元的资金，创下行业纪录，其业务正在印度和非洲不断扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/world-s-biggest-mini-grid-firm-aims-to-raise-400-million-plans-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
